OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,FA prison reform charity has described
OL,7,FWinchester Prison as "truly squalid"
OL,8,Ffollowing the release of an official
OL,9,Freport by HM Inspectorate of Prisons.
OL,11,FThe Howard League for Penal Reform
OL,12,Fsaid the full report, issued on
OL,13,FTuesday, raised questions about the
OL,14,Fleadership of the prison and about the
OL,15,Fgovernment's plans to build more jails.
