OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,FThe inspection was carried out in
OL,7,FOctober and conditions were found to
OL,8,Fbe so bad that an urgent notification
OL,9,Fwas released. This gave the Secretary
OL,10,Fof State for Justice 28 days to
OL,11,Frespond with an action plan for
OL,12,Fimprovement.
OL,14,FWinchester is a category B reception
OL,15,Fprison, capable of holding up to 649
OL,16,Fadult male prisoners.
OL,18,FThe report described the prison, which
OL,19,Fhad been inspected four times since
OL,20,F2016, as "persistently underachieving".
