OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,F"Although we acknowledged at the time
OL,7,Fof the inspection that the prison
OL,8,Fgroup director recognised the
OL,9,Fchallenges and shortcomings of the
OL,10,Fjail and that the HMPPS Prison
OL,11,FPerformance Support Programme had very
OL,12,Frecently drawn up a delivery plan,
OL,13,Fneither had yet had any effect.
OL,15,F"The poor outcomes at Winchester
OL,16,Frepresent systemic failings under the
OL,17,Foversight of HMPPS. If the prison is
OL,18,Fto provide decent living conditions,
OL,19,Fimprove safety and security and
OL,20,Foperate effectively, it will require
OL,21,Fsustained support and investment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
