OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,FAndrea Coomber KC, Chief Executive of
OL,7,Fthe Howard League for Penal Reform,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is one of the worst
OL,9,Freports on a prison that I have ever
OL,10,Fread, and the photographs of filthy
OL,11,Ftoilets, broken windows and mouldy
OL,12,Fwalls tell their own story. A truly
OL,13,Fsqualid, overcrowded Victorian jail `
OL,14,Feven to the point that some cells do
OL,15,Fnot have electricity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
