OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,F"Winchester received an awful
OL,7,Finspection report in 2022, but things
OL,8,Fhave gone from bad to worse. This
OL,9,Fraises important questions about the
OL,10,Fleadership of the prison, both locally
OL,11,Fand nationally, and about the
OL,12,Fgovernment's plans to build more jails
OL,13,Fwhen the ones we have are failing so
OL,14,Fmiserably."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
