OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,FCommenting on the report, Steve
OL,7,FGillan, Prison Officers Association
OL,8,FGeneral Secretary, said: "This report
OL,9,Finto HMP Winchester is a damning
OL,10,Fexample of the crisis that is playing
OL,11,Fout in Prisons across the country.
OL,12,FMany of the issues raised by the
OL,13,FInspectors have been raised repeatedly
OL,14,Fby our members who work on the
OL,15,Ffrontline.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
