OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,F"Once again, Inspectors have
OL,7,Fidentified the failure of HMPPS
OL,8,Fleadership to deliver improvements at
OL,9,Fthis Prison. It is the role of prison
OL,10,Fservice leaders to drive improvement
OL,11,Fclearly, they have failed in their
OL,12,Fduty to do so and this has major
OL,13,Fconsequences for both staff and
OL,14,Fprisoners.
OL,16,F"The stark declaration that the
OL,17,F'prison is unsafe' is of huge concern
OL,18,Fto the POA; our members at this Prison
OL,19,Fare being exposed to high levels of
OL,20,Fserious assaults, a completely
OL,21,Funacceptable situation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
