OL,3,C'Truly squalid': Prison reform charity
OL,4,Creacts to Winchester Prison report
OL,6,F"I wish that I could say that this
OL,7,Freport is a one off but sadly it
OL,8,Fisn't."
OL,10,FLord Timpson, Minister for Prisons and
OL,11,FProbation, said: "The dire situation
OL,12,Fat Winchester highlighted by the Chief
OL,13,FInspector is yet another symptom of
OL,14,Fthe prison crisis we inherited.
OL,16,F"We are supporting the prison and its
OL,17,Fstaff who are working hard to deliver
OL,18,Fimprovements in challenging
OL,19,Fcircumstances. This action plan will
OL,20,Fensure they have the support they
OL,21,Fneed."
